The AWS Cloud/Devops Engineer will be working with the engineering team and focusing on AWS infrastructure and automation. This role will maintain, evolve and secure our AWS infrastructure in support of critical compliance solutions.

-English fluency required.

Duties & Responsibilities:
* Manage AWS support teams to ensure existing solutions meet stakeholder expectations and are compliant with internal Cloud policies

* Ensure configuration and compliance with configuration management tools (AWS Config etc.)

* Administer and troubleshoot Linux based systems, knowledge of Windows systems.

* Troubleshoot problems across a wide array of services and functional areas

* Build and maintain operational tools for deployment, monitoring, and analysis of AWS infrastructure and systems

* Perform infrastructure cost analysis and optimization

Qualifications:
